column2: SELECT U.up_id, S.*  FROM #upLoad U CROSS APPLY (SELECT Objid FROM   dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq( U.up_ra ,U.up_dec ,U.up_sep )) S  SELECT TOP #   p.ra,p.dec, p.run,p.rerun,p.camCol,p.field,p.obj  FROM ..Star AS p  JOIN #x AS x ON x.objID=p.objID  JOIN #upload AS u ON u.up_id = x.up_id   WHERE  p.psfMag_r < #   ORDER BY x.up_id
